&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析&#34;&gt;分析&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;当$H(s) = -1$时，输入与反馈相抵消，留下&lt;strong&gt;噪声&lt;/strong&gt;被不断放大&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$A = \dfrac{H(s)}{1 + H(s)}$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;barkhausen-criteria&#34;&gt;Barkhausen criteria&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;若$\angle H(j\omega_0) = \pi$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_X = \sum_{i=0}^{\infin} |H(j\omega_0)|^i V_0
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;若$|H(j\omega_0)| \ge 1$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_X 发散
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;若$|H(j\omega_0)| &amp;lt; 1$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_0 = \dfrac{V_X}{1 - H(j\omega_0)}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Barkhausen Criteria&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;电路振荡的&lt;strong&gt;必要不充分&lt;/strong&gt;条件&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
\angle H(j\omega_0) &amp;amp;= \pi \\
|H(j\omega_0)| &amp;amp;\ge 1
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;ring-oscillators&#34;&gt;Ring Oscillators&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-stage-ring-oscillators&#34;&gt;3-Stage Ring Oscillators&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;电路&#34;&gt;电路&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1436&#34;
	height=&#34;582&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/2_hud6cf15a53f996ecbecb5d1b088f595d3_79965_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/2_hud6cf15a53f996ecbecb5d1b088f595d3_79965_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;246&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;592px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析-1&#34;&gt;分析&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;不考虑&lt;strong&gt;GD电容&lt;/strong&gt;的增益&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
H(s) &amp;amp;= - \frac{A_0^3}{(1+\dfrac{s}{\omega_0})^3}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;为了使得总相位差达到&lt;strong&gt;180度&lt;/strong&gt;，每一阶段都要分担&lt;strong&gt;60度&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
tan^{-1} \frac{\omega_{osc}}{\omega_0} &amp;amp;= 60^o \\
\therefore \omega_{osc} &amp;amp;= \sqrt{3} \omega_0 \\
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Loop Gain&lt;/strong&gt; $A\beta = 1$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在该电路中，显然$\beta=1$&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
\frac{A_0^3}{[\sqrt{1 + (\dfrac{\omega_{osc}}{\omega_0})^2}]^3} &amp;amp;= 1 \\
\therefore A_0 &amp;amp;= 2
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;4&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
A &amp;amp;= \frac{H(s)}{1 + H(s)} \\
&amp;amp;= \frac{- \dfrac{A_0^3}{(1+\dfrac{s}{\omega_0})^3}}{1 + \dfrac{A_0^3}{(1+\dfrac{s}{\omega_0})^3}}\\
&amp;amp;= - \frac{A_0^3}{(1 + \dfrac{s}{\omega_0})^3 + A_0^3} \\
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;5&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Poles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
(1 + \frac{s}{\omega_0})^3 + A_0^3 &amp;amp;= (1 + \frac{s}{\omega_0} + A_0) [(1+\frac{s}{\omega_0})^2  - (1 + \frac{s}{\omega_0})A_0 + A_0^2] \\
Let \ D &amp;amp;= 0 \\
s_1 &amp;amp;= (-A-1)\omega_0 \\
s_{2,3} &amp;amp;= [\frac{A_0 (1 \pm j\sqrt 3)}{2} - 1]\omega_0
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;6&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;输出电压&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;忽略$s_1$的影响&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
V_{out}(t) &amp;amp;= ae^{\dfrac{A_0-2}{2}\omega_0 t}cos(\frac{A_0 \sqrt 3}{2} \omega_0 t)
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;lc-oscillators&#34;&gt;LC Oscillators&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;crossed-coupled-oscillators&#34;&gt;Crossed-Coupled Oscillators&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;图示-1&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1320&#34;
	height=&#34;824&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/3_hu53a82da5684d5b2d49ea52c83201e9ef_102285_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/3_hu53a82da5684d5b2d49ea52c83201e9ef_102285_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;384px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
A_v &amp;amp;= g_{m1}R_P g_{m2}R_P \ge 1
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;改进1&#34;&gt;改进1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/9.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1292&#34;
	height=&#34;944&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/9_hu699a03d63a88d27c6c32e52a524f112a_113416_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/9_hu699a03d63a88d27c6c32e52a524f112a_113416_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;136&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;328px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;改成了&lt;strong&gt;Differential Pair&lt;/strong&gt;，并增加了&lt;strong&gt;恒流源&lt;/strong&gt;，从而提高了电路的稳定性&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;此时的$V_{DD}$可以被当作&lt;strong&gt;控制电压&lt;/strong&gt;，从而形成一个&lt;strong&gt;VCO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
C_{DB} &amp;amp;= \frac{C_{DB0}}{(1 + \dfrac{V_{DD}}{\phi_m})^m} \\
\omega_{out} &amp;amp;= \frac{1}{\sqrt{L_p C_{DB}}} \\
\therefore K_{VCO} &amp;amp;= \frac{\partial \omega_{out}}{\partial V_{DD}} \\
&amp;amp;= \frac{\partial \omega_{out}}{\partial C_{DB}} \frac{\partial C_{DB}}{\partial V_{DD}} \\
&amp;amp;= \frac{m}{2\phi_B (1+\dfrac{V_{DD}}{\phi_B})^{m+1}}\omega_{out}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$m$ 是一个与MOSFET结构有关的常数，通常取值在0.5到1.5之间&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$\phi_m$ 是 MOSFET 的表面势垒&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;改进2&#34;&gt;改进2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/10.png&#34;
	width=&#34;762&#34;
	height=&#34;1210&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/10_hue60e4fe9310d52883e6404225371f942_95810_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/10_hue60e4fe9310d52883e6404225371f942_95810_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;62&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;151px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;合并两边的电路&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;colpitts-oscillators&#34;&gt;Colpitts Oscillators&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;电路-1&#34;&gt;电路&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;704&#34;
	height=&#34;1070&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/4_hu165185a51f8592fafbabe79002bf7453_75858_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/4_hu165185a51f8592fafbabe79002bf7453_75858_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;65&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;157px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析-2&#34;&gt;分析&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;小信号模型&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/5.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1586&#34;
	height=&#34;632&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/5_hu22704ca8a68fa40db3eec8d3d666c703_83629_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/5_hu22704ca8a68fa40db3eec8d3d666c703_83629_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;250&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;602px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;KVL &amp;amp; KCL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
V_1 &amp;amp;= - (I_{in} - \frac{V_{out}}{R_P} - \frac{V_{out}}{sL_P})\frac{1}{sC_1} \\
0 &amp;amp;= -g_mV_1 + (V_{out} - V_1)sC_2 + \frac{V_{out}}{sL_P} + \frac{V_{out}}{R_P}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transresistance Gain&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
A_R &amp;amp;= \frac{V_{out}}{I_{in}} \\
&amp;amp;= &amp;hellip;
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;4&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;虚部无穷大 $\Longrightarrow$ 振荡&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;令虚部分母为0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;又$R_P(C_1 + C_2) \gg g_mR_P$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
\therefore g_mR_P &amp;amp;= \frac{C_1}{C_2}(1+ \frac{C_2}{C_1})^2 \ge 4
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;one-port-oscillators&#34;&gt;One-Port Oscillators&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;定义与图示&#34;&gt;定义与图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/11.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1138&#34;
	height=&#34;524&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/11_hu7a2e4be1f5744e08d7f9995e83d830dd_57360_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/11_hu7a2e4be1f5744e08d7f9995e83d830dd_57360_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;217&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;521px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;与&lt;strong&gt;RLC电路&lt;/strong&gt;并联的&lt;strong&gt;负电阻&lt;/strong&gt;可能产生&lt;strong&gt;振荡&lt;/strong&gt;的电路&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;cg--rlc&#34;&gt;CG + RLC&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/12.png&#34;
	width=&#34;800&#34;
	height=&#34;636&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/12_huc2ef7ee3997fc23ef7f49103c4147aa6_50159_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/12_huc2ef7ee3997fc23ef7f49103c4147aa6_50159_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;125&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;301px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;voltage-controlled-oscillators&#34;&gt;Voltage-Controlled Oscillators&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;理想压控振荡器&#34;&gt;理想压控振荡器&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
\omega_{out} &amp;amp;= \omega_0 + K_{VCO} V_{cont}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gain/Sensitivity: $K_{VCO}$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tuning Range: 定义域$[\omega_1,\omega_2]$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;为了达到尽可能大的范围，$K_{VCO}$要&lt;strong&gt;尽可能大&lt;/strong&gt;；为了减小$V_{cont}$带来的噪声，$K_{VCO}$要&lt;strong&gt;尽可能小&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;重要参数&#34;&gt;重要参数&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Center Frequency&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;受&lt;strong&gt;温度&lt;/strong&gt;等环境因素影响，可能产生&lt;strong&gt;2倍&lt;/strong&gt;以上的波动&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Tuning Range&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gain&lt;/strong&gt;一般要大于期望的&lt;strong&gt;斜率&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Tuning Linearity&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;为了使系统&lt;strong&gt;稳定&lt;/strong&gt;，必须使得$K_{VCO}$尽可能&lt;strong&gt;恒定&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Power Dissipation&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;功耗要尽量&lt;strong&gt;低&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Output Amplitude&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;输出幅度要尽量&lt;strong&gt;大&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Supply &amp;amp; CM Rejection &amp;amp; Output Signal Purity&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;噪声要尽量小&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;一个简单的vco&#34;&gt;一个简单的VCO&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;电路-2&#34;&gt;电路&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1188&#34;
	height=&#34;676&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/6_hu90b30d465ab4d1c3688376d559c83468_73103_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/14.-oscillators/6_hu90b30d465ab4d1c3688376d559c83468_73103_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;175&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;421px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析-3&#34;&gt;分析&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
\tau_1 &amp;amp;= RC_L \\
&amp;amp;= \frac{C_L}{\mu_p C_{ox} (W/L)&lt;em&gt;3 (V&lt;/em&gt;{DD} - V_{cont} - |V_{THP}|)} \\
\because Delay \ T_D &amp;amp;\propto \tau_1 \\
\therefore f_{osc} &amp;amp;\propto \frac{1}{\tau_1} \\
f_{osc} &amp;amp;\propto \frac{\mu_p C_{ox} (W/L)&lt;em&gt;3 (V&lt;/em&gt;{DD} - V_{cont} - |V_{THP}|)}{C_L}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;但是$K_{VCO}$过大&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;改进&#34;&gt;改进&lt;/h3&gt;
